src:
Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 Midday' game
05 Nov 2019, 18:04 by The Associated Press
CLEVELAND (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday afternoon's drawing of the Ohio Lottery's "Pick 4 Midday" game were:
6-4-9-1
(six, four, nine, one)
